Manage local like log

Usage:
  radio log show
  radio log tail [--lines N]
  radio log --help

Commands:
  show
    Show the entire like log

  tail
    Show the last few rows of the like log

Options:
  -l --lines N
    Number of lines to show [default: 5]

  -h --help
    Show this help

Examples:
  radio log show
  radio log tail
  radio log tail --lines 10
  radio log sort
